{"tid":111521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"溝過幾次有仔嘅女，你問我答","createTime":"2017-02-07T12:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T16:43:07.000Z","uid":335,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e64efb36b158dbad730b141a0ce7daeadcffcf","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"預左俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開黎純粹想呻下。有時錯嘅時間遇到對嘅人真係好無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有啲情況我認我係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1111d261be40780bc54bb5983483eadbe5f7e2","tid":111521,"uid":82198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"點樣溝？<br />\n對方有冇受？<br />\n最親密做過咩野？<br />\n條仔知唔知？"},{"pid":"b682319df06285af1257d8efbb98d791752f4da7","tid":111521,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"巴打點散？係咪每次都畀條女戴帽"},{"pid":"722ce8552a765cbad4afb3454253e7d60b4ddc1c","tid":111521,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c461f92d5e3a433e2f60f4e784e282052f45af28","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣溝？<br />\n對方有冇受？<br />\n最親密做過咩野？<br />\n條仔知唔知？</blockquote><br />\n個個都唔同方法識到啵<br />\n有受有唔受（其實有啲有仔我都唔知，有個呃鳩我話冇）<br />\n上床<br />\n唔知掛，so far未俾人打死（有都打死都唔會認）"},{"pid":"5c19b535a599d15c4c8a87fcb93845f6de4aa398","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打點散？係咪每次都畀條女戴帽</blockquote><br />\n有啲根本連正式一齊都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前有個就俾過半頂帽我戴"},{"pid":"9f696f7b9d170938035060d23a6618fa8628bbc5","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0