/>"},{"pid":"eeae224d7edaabbf2cfb1a051d235ee71334865d","tid":111521,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"巴打一定好靚仔"},{"pid":"2145e1a0cee288b74e06a05dc1273c83a3d9faa9","tid":111521,"uid":76383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連兄弟嘅女都唔放過<br />\n不過唔會再發生呢種事</blockquote><br />\n點解唔會再發生？見過鬼怕黑？</blockquote><br />\n我而家睇兄弟朋友重啲，以前爭啲冇左個好朋友，我超級後悔。好彩佢之後原諒左我</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪條女既男友唔係你兄弟就會再出手"},{"pid":"fe786ced1e9ff8ca96a000896d2d6eb269a3bf2c","tid":111521,"uid":1292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216a8d030c172cb4e439b6ee4c37ab8b9429886e","tid":111521,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"可以分享下你的策略或者手段嗎？"},{"pid":"4c6d6acf76da517c4923526bf9584b25bb4cc5b2","tid":111521,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2a28f3a52682889f90c93d9d97da19ee7c5c9152","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都想搶女神返黎，求巴打教路</blockquote><br />\n佢有仔？</blockquote><br />\n係呀，有仔，怕左4,5年拖</blockquote><br />\n要睇好多環境因素先判斷到啵"},{"pid":"cf36985214f3280746c674a1171d4311ae0c0a7d","tid":111521,"uid":76383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都想搶女神返黎，求巴打教路</blockquote><br />\n佢有仔？</blockquote><br />\n係呀，有仔，怕左4,5年拖</blockquote><br />\n要睇好多環境因素先判斷到啵</blockquote><br />\n例如呢？"},{"pid":"6c23b8437b4094297ade4b63b12364124a5b90cb","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下搶人條女番黎會唔會好驚佢有日都會比人搶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時我會諗今日佢俾帽佢條仔，他朝我都避免唔到<br />\n所以有啲我溝落都唔覺得會一齊到"},{"pid":"2c1d44bd88434a8866c4eec7db2fee9b4f23d2f8","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打一定好靚仔</blockquote><br />\n靚仔只係好似你打機嘅buff，有嘅或會助你一臂之力，冇嘅亦唔代表你唔會成功"},{"pid":"a81adebe218e6a2376d8618715af3c9f48435c7d","tid":111521,"uid":20669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb2558e018546ddfbefa2c8ec792e53847bf4b3","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連兄弟嘅女都唔放過<br />\n不過唔會再發生呢種事</blockquote><br />\n點解唔會再發生？見過鬼怕黑？</blockquote><br />\n我而家睇兄弟朋友重啲，以前爭啲冇左個好朋友，我超級後悔。好彩佢之後原諒左我</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪條女既男友唔係你兄弟就會再出手</blockquote><br />\n如果個女仔條仔我唔識嘅就係"},{"pid":"af6da1bb2d0e83034c46c7a12e6c64bf47fb0d5c","tid":111521,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣未知住，但我覺得有報應喇。我最鍾意嘅人佢飛完我一次又一次，心都死埋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}